<template>
  <v-card>
    <v-card-title>
      <v-btn color="success">Nuevo Registro</v-btn>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-text-field
        v-model="search"
        label="Buscar"
        append-icon="search"
        single-line
        hide-details
      ></v-text-field>
    </v-card-title>
    <v-data-table
      :headers="headers"
      :items="desserts"
      :search="search"
    ></v-data-table>
  </v-card>
</template>


<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        search: '',
        headers: [
          {
            text: 'Mes',
            align: 'left',
            sortable: false,
            value: 'mes',

          { text: 'Eficacia', value: 'eficacia' },
          { text: 'Causa asignable Longitud Perforacion', value: 'causa' },
          { text: 'AVANCE Diario', value: 'avance' },
          { text: '>=2.9', value: 'mayor' },
          { text: '<2.9', value: 'menor' },
          { text: 'LEI', value: 'lei' },
          { text: 'Objetivo', value: 'obj' },
          { text: 'N° Taladros', value: 'Ntal' },
          { text: 'Kg Explosivo', value: 'kgExplo' },

 },
